---
layout: landing-layout.njk
title: ""
description: "HomeStart helps first-time buyers plan savings and cash-to-close—optional bank linking, not a lender. Join the waitlist."
---

{% from "icons-features.njk" import icon %}

<header class="site-header" id="site-header" data-header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    {% include "brand-logo.njk" %}
    <nav aria-label="Primary">
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="#how-it-works">How it works</a></li>
        <li><a href="#waitlist" class="nav-cta">Join waitlist</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<main id="main">
  <section class="section hero" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <p class="hero-eyebrow">{{ site.name }}</p>
        <h1 id="hero-heading">Your home plan, finally in one place.</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">A calm planning app for first-time buyers—savings, full cash-to-close clarity, and a guided roadmap. Not a lender. Not listings.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="btn btn--primary" href="#waitlist">Join the waitlist</a>
          <a class="btn btn--secondary" href="#how-it-works">Learn more</a>
        </div>
        <p class="hero-note">Optional bank linking via Plaid—only if you want real balances in the picture.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-mock phone-mock--loading" data-phone-mock aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="mock-frame">
          <div class="mock-screen mock-screen--animated">
            <div class="phone-layer phone-layer--splash">
              <img class="phone-splash-gif" src="/images/splash.gif" alt="" width="200" height="200" decoding="async">
            </div>
            <div class="phone-layer phone-layer--app">
              <div class="app-preview">
                <div class="app-preview__status">
                  <span>9:41</span>
                  <span class="app-preview__dots">●●●●</span>
                </div>
                <div class="app-preview__tabs" role="presentation">
                  <span class="app-preview__tab">Roadmap</span>
                  <span class="app-preview__tab app-preview__tab--active">Plan</span>
                  <span class="app-preview__tab">Accounts</span>
                </div>
                <div class="app-preview__card">
                  <div class="app-preview__card-head">
                    <div class="app-preview__icon" aria-hidden="true">
                      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M3 21h18M5 21V7l8-4v18M19 21V11l-6-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <p class="app-preview__kicker">Linked home fund</p>
                      <p class="app-preview__title">Your savings in one place</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <p class="app-preview__amount">$47,200</p>
                  <p class="app-preview__caption">Counted from linked accounts toward this goal</p>
                  <div class="app-preview__bar-wrap">
                    <div class="app-preview__bar" style="--p: 62%;"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="app-preview__bar-labels">
                    <span>62% of full cash goal</span>
                    <span>Goal $76k</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="app-preview__pills">
                    <span><strong>2</strong> Institutions</span>
                    <span><strong>3</strong> Counting</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="app-preview__cta">Manage home fund →</div>
                </div>
                <p class="app-preview__hint">Sample screen—inspired by the real dashboard.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--tight trust" aria-label="Trust">
    <div class="trust-inner">
      <div class="trust-item">
        <strong>Built for first-time buyers</strong>
        Education and preparation—not a mortgage application.
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <strong>Planning tool only</strong>
        Estimates are illustrative. Real terms come from your lender.
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <strong>Your data, your choice</strong>
        Link accounts with Plaid or track savings manually.
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="trust-placeholder section" style="margin-bottom:0;max-width:720px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">Room for quotes or stats when you have them—early access users, press, or partner logos.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="features" aria-labelledby="features-heading">
    <p class="section-label">Features</p>
    <h2 id="features-heading">Built to keep you moving</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">Everything ties back to one goal: closing with confidence—without drowning in spreadsheets.</p>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <article class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("savings") }}</div>
        <h3>Smarter savings pace</h3>
        <p>See what it takes to hit down payment, closing, reserves, and moving costs—then adjust your monthly plan as life changes.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("cash") }}</div>
        <h3>Full cash-to-close, not just “20% down”</h3>
        <p>Most apps stop at down payment. HomeStart rolls in closing, post-close reserves, and setup cash so the target matches reality.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("afford") }}</div>
        <h3>Affordability you can feel</h3>
        <p>Map estimated housing next to rent, income, and debts—so you understand monthly fit before you fall in love with a price.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap feature-icon-wrap--accent" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("link") }}</div>
        <h3>Link banks—or don’t</h3>
        <p>Optional Plaid keeps balances fresh; manual entries work too. You choose how much to connect.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("roadmap") }}</div>
        <h3>Roadmap, not random tabs</h3>
        <p>Milestones and bite-sized lessons so “what’s next?” is always clear—especially when you’re new to the process.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="how-it-works" aria-labelledby="how-heading">
    <p class="section-label">How it works</p>
    <h2 id="how-heading">Three steps</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">Start simple. Refine as you go.</p>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <h3>Start with your finances</h3>
        <p>Income, rent, debts, and what you already have saved—so the plan matches reality.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <h3>Set your home target</h3>
        <p>Draft a price or monthly payment comfort, then layer taxes, insurance, and timing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <h3>Track progress over time</h3>
        <p>Update savings, link accounts if you want, and follow the roadmap to launch day.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="waitlist" aria-labelledby="waitlist-heading">
    <p class="section-label">Early access</p>
    <div class="waitlist">
      <h2 id="waitlist-heading">Get early access</h2>
      <p>Be first on the App Store list. No spam—launch updates only.</p>
      <form class="waitlist-form" id="waitlist-form" novalidate>
        <div class="field-wrap">
          <label class="visually-hidden" for="waitlist-email">Email address</label>
          <input type="email" id="waitlist-email" name="email" autocomplete="email" placeholder="you@email.com" required inputmode="email">
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary btn--submit" id="waitlist-submit">Join waitlist</button>
      </form>
      <div class="waitlist-status" id="waitlist-status" role="status" aria-live="polite"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <span class="footer-brand">{{ site.name }}</span>
    <ul class="footer-links">
      <li><a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy</a></li>
      <li><a href="/terms-of-service/">Terms</a></li>
      <li><a href="/security-overview/">Security</a></li>
      <li><a href="mailto:{{ site.supportEmail }}">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="footer-meta">© {{ site.copyrightYear }} {{ site.companyLegalName }}</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
  (function () {
    var h = document.getElementById("site-header");
    if (!h) return;
    function tick() {
      h.classList.toggle("is-scrolled", window.scrollY > 8);
    }
    tick();
    window.addEventListener("scroll", tick, { passive: true });
  })();
</script>
